                    <span id="c-126577442" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-126577442" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="126577442">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/R.Lee/">[已注销]</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2009-06-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">避免被这个腐败的世界庸俗化。精神上要有高尚的追求。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="892004353">
